
A userscript that tracks and displays time spent on configured websites. Shows a persistent timer overlay to help monitor your daily usage.

## Installation

### Installing Greasemonkey Scripts

**Chrome/Edge/Brave:**
1. Install [Tampermonkey](https://www.tampermonkey.net/)
2. Click on `tally.user.js` in this repository
3. Click "Raw" button
4. Tampermonkey will prompt you to install the script

**Firefox:**
1. Install [Greasemonkey](https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/greasemonkey/) or [Tampermonkey](https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/tampermonkey/)
2. Click on `tally.user.js` in this repository
3. Click "Raw" button
4. The extension will prompt you to install the script

**Safari:**
1. Install [Userscripts](https://apps.apple.com/us/app/userscripts/id1463298887) extension
2. Enable the extension in Safari preferences
3. Click on `tally.user.js` and "Raw" button to install

